      <h1>Emmanuel <em>School</em></h1>
      <p class="deck">We are very proud of our strong connections with Emmanuel School — our neighbour and partner in faith and learning.</p>
      <div class="meta-row"><div class="item"><div class="k">Together</div><div class="v">Weekly Collective Worship</div></div><div class="item"><div class="k">Eucharist</div><div class="v">First Monday of the month</div></div><div class="item"><div class="k">Admissions</div><div class="v">By the church route</div></div></div>
